Package datacube.search.share.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataFactory
    This class serves for testing purpose
    Create testing data object such as IDictionary and IDataCube with their input parameters
    Dictionary
    This class is an extension of AbstractDictionary and is an implementation of IDictionary
    Search2DAllDimension
    This is an implementation of AbstractSearch2D class
    This class will search the given 2D array and the giving string through 3 dimensions from any directions
    Search2DDiagonal
    This is an implementation of AbstractSearch2D class
    This class will search the given 2D array and the given string in diagonal dimension from any directions
    SearchArray
    This class implements search functions and methods to separate and collect 2D arrays from 3D arrays
    Some search functions refers to http://www.kosbie.net/cmu/fall-08/15-100/handouts/notes-two-dimensional-arrays.html#deepToString
    SearchParallelPlane1
    This class is an extension of AbstractSearch3D
    Invoke all scheduled unit tasks that the given word will be searched in the planes of x = x0 + 1, y = y0 - 1, z = z0 + 1
    SearchParallelPlane2
    This class is an extension of AbstractSearch3D
    Invoke all scheduled unit tasks that the given word will be searched in the planes of x = x0 + 1, y = y0 + 1, z = z0 + 1
    SearchParallelPlane3
    This class is an extension of AbstractSearch3D
    Invoke all scheduled unit tasks that the given word will be searched in the planes of x = x0 + 1, y = y0 - 1, z = z0 - 1 in execution process
    SearchParallelPlane4
    This class is an extension of AbstractSearch3D class
    Invoke all scheduled unit tasks that the given word will be searched in the planes of x = x0 + 1, y = y0 + 1, z = z0 - 1 in execution process
